Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object recognition systems and membership functions for evaluating physical properties of objects. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper introduces a learning component for the recognition system. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the learning algorithm used in the paper falls under this category. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is possible as the paper mentions the use of the recognition system in robotics applications. 
5. cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also possible as the paper discusses the implementation of the learning component in the Gruff system.
